of work that I think we've seen

00:01:48.173 --> 00:01:49.006
and in the way in which

00:01:49.006 --> 00:01:51.630
these ideas kind of layer onto each other.

00:01:51.630 --> 00:01:53.730
You know I think it was really incredible

00:01:53.730 --> 00:01:56.370
when we were seeing the Kennis brothers

00:01:56.370 --> 00:01:57.840
and you know...

00:01:59.597 --> 00:02:01.760
You start to hear the kinds of,

00:02:01.760 --> 00:02:04.440
the depth and complexity that is brought

00:02:04.440 --> 00:02:08.480
