00:02:18.370 --> 00:02:21.500
based on best practices

00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:24.280
but that involves the development

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:28.530
and thinking about all
the other kind of factors

00:02:28.530 --> 00:02:30.670
that would go into you know

00:02:30.670 --> 00:02:35.670
what an early human or
other kind of hominid life

00:02:37.500 --> 00:02:39.850
might actually consist of

00:02:39.850 --> 00:02:42.380
and then how the kind
of aesthetic criteria

00:02:42.380 --> 00:02:45.070
goes into creating
something that can actually

00:02:45.070 --> 00:02:47.723
engage our imagination as we look at it.

00:02:48.940 --> 00:02:52.703
And in all the work that I
think we've heard about today,

00:02:54.190 --> 00:02:57.870
recognizing the necessity to be able

00:02:57.870 --> 00:03:02.870
