broadly across disciplines

00:03:03.396 --> 00:03:07.050
such that you know
taking on a question like

00:03:07.050 --> 00:03:10.450
you know the human origins,
you might come at it

00:03:10.450 --> 00:03:14.460
from a disciplinary expertise

00:03:14.460 --> 00:03:17.170
but because you're entering into such

00:03:17.170 --> 00:03:20.070
unknown territory, you know the vectors

00:03:20.070 --> 00:03:25.070
that you try to connect that are beyond

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:28.150
the specifics that you
bring to the question

00:03:28.150 --> 00:03:30.280
are the ones that possibly lead you

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:33.920
to new kinds of answers about it.

