00:30:41.660 --> 00:30:44.930
the world that becomes a
little bit more problematic.

00:30:44.930 --> 00:30:47.820
I think people are, and
scientists are aware

00:30:47.820 --> 00:30:49.430
that these might create some

00:30:50.950 --> 00:30:53.710
concerns in parts of the society

00:30:53.710 --> 00:30:56.170
but nonetheless we are doing that

00:30:56.170 --> 00:30:58.120
to answer from the mental questions

00:30:58.120 --> 00:31:01.810
and my lab focuses on
neurological disorders

00:31:01.810 --> 00:31:03.573
so the aim is good.

00:31:03.573 --> 00:31:08.573
Same rationale could be applied
