00:31:25.210 --> 00:31:27.230
or are more intelligent if we figure out

00:31:27.230 --> 00:31:30.060
what is the biological basis of that

00:31:30.060 --> 00:31:34.070
so it's up to the society
to put the threshold.

00:31:34.070 --> 00:31:36.670
In my experience I think most scientist

00:31:36.670 --> 00:31:38.520
would agree with that, in the beginning

00:31:38.520 --> 00:31:40.740
of a new technology there always

00:31:40.740 --> 00:31:45.340
some turmoil about what
the consequences of that

00:31:45.340 --> 00:31:47.250
but this is slowly will go away

00:31:47.250 --> 00:31:51.210
as the scientist shows
how useful are those.

