So the same thing for blood transfusion

00:31:53.300 --> 00:31:57.560
for organ transplant,
they all raise red flags

00:31:57.560 --> 00:32:01.170
and now we do it quite common to do it.

00:32:01.170 --> 00:32:05.108
So I think the idea of brain
organize in genome editing

00:32:05.108 --> 00:32:06.970
