imagination happening in childhood,

00:33:12.390 --> 00:33:14.890
this is how we see it
happening in other species,

00:33:14.890 --> 00:33:17.230
this is the kind of condition of humanity

00:33:17.230 --> 00:33:20.680
that leads us to kind of have this genetic

00:33:20.680 --> 00:33:24.909
