00:37:00.630 --> 00:37:04.370
They love at the pretend

00:37:05.720 --> 00:37:09.770
unlike Piaget who's just
sort of got muddled.

00:37:09.770 --> 00:37:13.730
So children have this area

00:37:13.730 --> 00:37:16.680
which they think is symbolic

00:37:16.680 --> 00:37:20.650
but they're conscious of it not being true

00:37:20.650 --> 00:37:24.740
on the other hand the kind of imagination

00:37:24.740 --> 00:37:27.910
takes place when people think you know

00:37:29.760 --> 00:37:33.080
their national identity or their clan

00:37:33.080 --> 00:37:37.400
or objects almost like
mountains in the world.

00:37:37.400 --> 00:37:42.150
They're not in a sense imaginary.

00:37:42.150 --> 00:37:44.010
This seems to be completely different

00:37:45.380 --> 00:37:49.337
and so the reason why I
don't like the term symbolic

00:37:49.337 --> 00:37:52.530
is that it muddles these
two things together.

00:37:52.530 --> 00:37:57.530
It muddles what we're
conscious of as a symbol

00:37:58.830 --> 00:38:02.220
