00:38:49.649 --> 00:38:51.680
So the question here is
that kind of imitation

00:38:51.680 --> 00:38:54.300
is that somehow grounded in imagination

00:38:54.300 --> 00:38:55.890
and I still don't know the answer

00:38:55.890 --> 00:38:58.560
but it's sort of a
different work around answer

00:38:58.560 --> 00:39:00.630
which is that neo natal imitation

00:39:00.630 --> 00:39:02.530
we think of mostly as a social reflex,

00:39:02.530 --> 00:39:05.610
it's something that happens
immediately after birth

00:39:05.610 --> 00:39:08.680
and what it does is it
sort of paves the way

00:39:08.680 --> 00:39:11.270
for all of the rest of social
cognition to come on board.

00:39:11.270 --> 00:39:14.370
Attention to faces following gaze,

00:39:14.370 --> 00:39:17.370
doing this kind of imitation
which makes your caregiver

00:39:17.370 --> 00:39:18.650
