00:39:18.650 --> 00:39:20.410
All of these things are really important

00:39:20.410 --> 00:39:22.250
for fostering social connection

00:39:22.250 --> 00:39:24.930
and so that later becomes complicated

00:39:24.930 --> 00:39:26.360
things like theory of
mind which absolutely

00:39:26.360 --> 00:39:28.570
involve imagining the
perspective of other people.

00:39:28.570 --> 00:39:30.990
So anyway I would say
that neo natal imitation

00:39:30.990 --> 00:39:34.460
is related to imagination but in a long

00:39:34.460 --> 00:39:36.920
sort of long trajectory as
opposed to sort of immediate

